@kibtes just correctly provide path to cudnn libraries. For example in .bashrc file put line: 
`export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="/path_to_your_cudnn/cuda/lib64":$LD_LIBRARY_PATH`
Then logout and login. Check path with command: `env | grep cundd`.
